snippet.title: [UM] Under the Weather Update - Part 1.
snippet.description:
Hold on to your hats! The first part of Uncompromising Modes 'Under the Weather' update has arrived, bringing along Tornadoes, Heavy Rains, Heatwaves, and much more!

Download Uncompromising Mode: https://steamcommunity.com/sharedfile...

Check out our Official Discord: https://discord.gg/DFnDuCyp8H

Browse our wiki for more info: https://uncompromisingmode.wiki.gg/
